To the Cook from Canada and anyone else with seafood allergies, most health food stores carry vegetarian fish sauce and oyster sauce made without any seafood products. If you can't find it, here is a link for a recipe http://www.geocities.com/dpham_001/cooking/fishsauce.html or http://www.recipecottage.com/vegetarian/fish-sauce.html

